criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        They will be included in this study children:

          -  aged 3 years and 6 years and 11 months;

          -  With complete primary dentition;

          -  Who have at least one active caries lesion score 3 or 4 ICDAS, in the occlusal molars
             surfaces.

          -  Who have assented to participate and whose parents have consented to their
             participation by signing the Instrument of Consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  who have medical and / or behavioral conditions that require special considerations
             regarding handling / treatment;

          -  who are involved in other research that may impact on this study;

          -  whose parents that not agree in participate.
